<subSubSection id="0C83650EFFE1FF85FF36FDC0FC7BFCE3" pageId="6" pageNumber="445" type="biology_ecology">
<paragraph id="44263685FFE1FF85FF36FDC0FDC9FD43" blockId="6.[166,1225,575,826]" pageId="6" pageNumber="445">
Host plants. 
<taxonomicName id="83994D06FFE1FF85FE7EFDBFFDD2FD80" authorityName="Rondani" authorityYear="1870" box="[403,619,575,601]" class="Insecta" family="Tephritidae" genus="Urophora" kingdom="Animalia" order="Diptera" pageId="6" pageNumber="445" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="jaculata">
<emphasis id="76EDEA97FFE1FF85FE7EFDBFFDD2FD80" box="[403,619,575,601]" italics="true" pageId="6" pageNumber="445">Urophora jaculata</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
infests 
<taxonomicName id="83994D06FFE1FF85FD25FDC0FC05FD80" box="[712,956,575,602]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Asteraceae" genus="Centaurea" kingdom="Plantae" order="Asterales" pageId="6" pageNumber="445" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="solstitialis">
<emphasis id="76EDEA97FFE1FF85FD25FDC0FC05FD80" box="[712,956,575,602]" italics="true" pageId="6" pageNumber="445">Centaurea solstitialis</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
in 
<collectingCountry id="3C8E7615FFE1FF85FC0BFDBFFBA2FD80" box="[998,1051,575,601]" name="Italy" pageId="6" pageNumber="445">Italy</collectingCountry>
and mainland 
<collectingCountry id="3C8E7615FFE1FF85FF4BFDDFFF41FDA0" box="[166,248,607,633]" name="Greece" pageId="6" pageNumber="445">Greece</collectingCountry>
and has been swept from other species of the subgenus 
<taxonomicName id="83994D06FFE1FF85FC5FFDE0FDD2FD43" authority="(Cardueae) (White &amp; Korneyev, 1989)" authorityName="White &amp; Korneyev" authorityYear="1989" baseAuthorityName="Cardueae" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Asteraceae" genus="Centaurea" kingdom="Plantae" order="Asterales" pageId="6" pageNumber="445" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="subGenus" subGenus="Solstitiaria">
<emphasis id="76EDEA97FFE1FF85FC5FFDE0FB95FDA3" box="[946,1068,608,634]" italics="true" pageId="6" pageNumber="445">Centaurea</emphasis>
(
<emphasis id="76EDEA97FFE1FF85FBADFDDFFB07FDA0" box="[1088,1214,607,633]" italics="true" pageId="6" pageNumber="445">Solstitiaria</emphasis>
) (Cardueae) (
<bibRefCitation id="20084B74FFE1FF85FED4FDFFFDDAFD43" author="White, I. M. &amp; Korneyev, V. A." box="[313,611,639,666]" pageId="6" pageNumber="445" pagination="327 - 374" refId="ref7720" refString="White, I. M., Korneyev, V. A. 1989. A revision of the Western Palearctic species of Urophora Robineau-Desvoidy (Diptera Tephritidae) Systematic Entomology, 14, 327 - 374. https: // doi. org / 10.1111 / j. 1365 - 3113.1989. tb 00289. x" type="journal article" year="1989">White &amp; Korneyev, 1989</bibRefCitation>
)
</taxonomicName>
.
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="44263685FFE1FF85FF36FD20FBABFD23" blockId="6.[166,1225,575,826]" pageId="6" pageNumber="445">
D i s t r i b u t i o n. 
<collectingCountry id="3C8E7615FFE1FF85FE70FD1FFE6DFD60" box="[413,468,671,697]" name="Italy" pageId="6" pageNumber="445">Italy</collectingCountry>
, 
<collectingCountry id="3C8E7615FFE1FF85FE32FD1FFD88FD60" box="[479,561,671,697]" name="Greece" pageId="6" pageNumber="445">Greece</collectingCountry>
(
<bibRefCitation id="20084B74FFE1FF85FDD2FD1FFCE3FD60" author="White, I. M. &amp; Clement, S. L." box="[575,858,671,697]" pageId="6" pageNumber="445" pagination="571 - 580" refId="ref7663" refString="White, I. M., Clement, S. L. 1987. Systematic notes on Urophora (Diptera, Tephritidae) species associated with Centaurea solstitialis (Asteraceae, Cardueae) and other Palaearctic weeds adventive in North America. Proceedings of the Entomological Society of Washington, 89, 571 - 580." type="journal article" year="1987">White &amp; Clement, 1987</bibRefCitation>
; 
<bibRefCitation id="20084B74FFE1FF85FC88FD1FFB34FD63" author="White, I. M. &amp; Korneyev, V. A." box="[869,1165,671,698]" pageId="6" pageNumber="445" pagination="327 - 374" refId="ref7720" refString="White, I. M., Korneyev, V. A. 1989. A revision of the Western Palearctic species of Urophora Robineau-Desvoidy (Diptera Tephritidae) Systematic Entomology, 14, 327 - 374. https: // doi. org / 10.1111 / j. 1365 - 3113.1989. tb 00289. x" type="journal article" year="1989">White &amp; Korneyev, 1989</bibRefCitation>
). Records from 
<collectingCountry id="3C8E7615FFE1FF85FEC3FD3FFE3AFD00" box="[302,387,703,729]" name="Turkey" pageId="6" pageNumber="445">Turkey</collectingCountry>
and Caucasus (
<bibRefCitation id="20084B74FFE1FF85FDD4FD3FFC89FD03" author="Norrbom, A. L. &amp; Carroll, L. E. &amp; Thompson, F. C. &amp; White, I. M. &amp; Freidberg, A." box="[569,816,703,730]" pageId="6" pageNumber="445" pagination="65 - 299" refId="ref7228" refString="Norrbom, A. L., Carroll, L. E., Thompson, F. C., White, I. M. &amp; Freidberg, A. 1999. Systematic Database of Names. In: Thompson, F. C., ed. Fruit Fly Expert Identification System and Systematic Information Database. Backhuis Publishers, Leiden, 65 - 299." type="book chapter" year="1999">Norrbom et al., 1999</bibRefCitation>
) are based on misidentifications of 
<taxonomicName id="83994D06FFE1FF85FF4BFD60FD4AFD23" authority="(Hering) (Korneyev &amp; White, 1992)" authorityName="Korneyev &amp; White" authorityYear="1992" baseAuthorityName="Hering" baseAuthorityYear="1938" box="[166,755,735,762]" class="Insecta" family="Tephritidae" genus="Urophora" kingdom="Animalia" order="Diptera" pageId="6" pageNumber="445" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="sirunaseva">
<emphasis id="76EDEA97FFE1FF85FF4BFD60FF02FD20" box="[166,187,736,761]" italics="true" pageId="6" pageNumber="445">U</emphasis>
. 
<emphasis id="76EDEA97FFE1FF85FF25FD60FEFAFD20" box="[200,323,736,761]" italics="true" pageId="6" pageNumber="445">sirunaseva</emphasis>
(Hering) (Korneyev &amp; White, 1992)
</taxonomicName>
. 
<collectingCountry id="3C8E7615FFE1FF85FD10FD60FCD1FD23" box="[765,872,736,762]" name="Morocco" pageId="6" pageNumber="445">Morocco</collectingCountry>
(
<emphasis id="76EDEA97FFE1FF85FC94FD5FFBB8FD20" bold="true" box="[889,1025,735,761]" pageId="6" pageNumber="445">first record</emphasis>
).
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="44263685FFE1FF85FF36FD7FFC7BFCE3" blockId="6.[166,1225,575,826]" pageId="6" pageNumber="445">
Remarks. This species was recorded by 
<bibRefCitation id="20084B74FFE1FF85FD5BFD7FFC5DFCC3" author="El Harym, Y. &amp; Belqat, B." box="[694,996,767,794]" pageId="6" pageNumber="445" pagination="137 - 171" refId="ref6286" refString="El Harym, Y., Belqat, B. 2017. First checklist of the fruit flies of Morocco, including new records (Diptera, Tephritidae). ZooKeys, 702, 137 - 171. https: // doi. org / 10.3897 / zookeys. 702.13368" type="journal article" year="2017">El Harym &amp; Belqat (2017)</bibRefCitation>
as “ 
<taxonomicName id="83994D06FFE1FF85FBFEFD7FFEB8FCE0" authorityName=": El Harym &amp; Belqat" authorityYear="2017" class="Insecta" family="Tephritidae" genus="Urophora" kingdom="Animalia" order="Diptera" pageId="6" pageNumber="445" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="mauritanica">
<emphasis id="76EDEA97FFE1FF85FBFEFD7FFEB8FCE0" italics="true" pageId="6" pageNumber="445">Urophora mauritanica</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
”, but after study of the aculeus was identified as 
<taxonomicName id="83994D06FFE1FF85FCD6FCA0FC02FCE0" authorityName="Rondani" authorityYear="1870" box="[827,955,799,826]" class="Insecta" family="Tephritidae" genus="Urophora" kingdom="Animalia" order="Diptera" pageId="6" pageNumber="445" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="jaculata">
<emphasis id="76EDEA97FFE1FF85FCD6FCA0FCE9FCE0" box="[827,848,800,825]" italics="true" pageId="6" pageNumber="445">U</emphasis>
. 
<emphasis id="76EDEA97FFE1FF85FCB0FC9FFC02FCE0" box="[861,955,799,825]" italics="true" pageId="6" pageNumber="445">jaculata</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
